title: Jedi Mind Tricks - The Amber Probe (EP) (1996)
description: Jedi Mind Tricks' first album.  Communion-The Crop Circle Thesis, Books Of Blood-The Coming Of Tan, and Neva Antiquated [Dark Jedi Remix] were all released the following year on The Psycho-Social, Chemical, Biological & Electro-Magnetic Manipulation of Human Consciousness, though Neva Antiquated [Dark Jedi Remix] was renamed for that release as simply Neva Antiquated.  The Neva Antiquated on Amber Probe is a unique version.
